[normal]3.11
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]In deciding whether harm to an ecosystem is significant, it is important for local authorities to bear in mind the following two principles of defining significant harm, which are established under the Environmental Protection Act:
